dct_description_sm: This tabular data, prepared by Data You Can Use, presents the Department of Housing and Urban Development (HUD) School Proficiency index by census block group in the city of Milwaukee, Wisconsin. The data is sourced from HUD - School Proficiency 2014, and utilizes 2010 Census block groups. For more information, please visit Data You Can Use.
